title: Robert Kelly: Diner Trash
description: Comedian and podcaster Robert Kelly joins us to talk trashy food at the diner, trashy vacations, and trashy muscle cars. Its a hot one!  You know Robert Kelly from Stand up comedy YKWD podcast, Comedy Central, Netflix, & Tonight Show. Rate. Review. Subscribe. Email questions: AreYouGarbage@gmail.com
